dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Johnny Turner. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Tammy. Can you provide me with the first three digits of your policy number?
Thank you. And could you please verify the last four digits of your Social Security number for security purposes?
Of course, it's six two one five.
Thank you, Tammy, for providing that information. How can I assist you today with your Old Stone Auto Insurance policy?
I have some questions about my policy coverage and premium payments.
I'd be happy to help with that. Thank you for reaching out, Tammy. Is there anything else you would like to know or discuss?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Johnny, for your assistance.
You're welcome, Tammy. Have a great day! Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance.
